{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c4421130a3f7239b3b2af2f6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "浴缸探险",
        "text_hash": "664d369cef3da3f17010728a685a6c11324e4ab09927d682f4d9eab86f8bda88",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_083d186694420350657ffcd6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "杰克的妈妈从浴室门口探进头来。杰克正放松地泡在浴缸里。",
        "text_hash": "266540362d53aeff2665159058fb69b6c79c554a24de815d9d81ab56060fa365",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3c64b566f8e80bda0333b965",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "洗澡时间是杰克一天中最喜欢的时刻。",
        "text_hash": "0805c602fa52c1e77363d8b97c8b5db9b095db7a3420bf69085a9b67258366b1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ed22375b792b373a3fabc2a5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“我一会儿就回来，”妈妈说。“一定要把耳朵后面洗干净。”",
        "text_hash": "d548c8091be5f5479b8cd898f8a0b106765d40719ccad4afd4db3ccaf56d05bc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_278188e79ec32eb09069d83d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "杰克看见水面上有个绿色、带尖刺的东西在动。",
        "text_hash": "428ae4bdfc14d6029e74a5cc5c61c6099f9ce3b4a57999d7c687dfeed541f8a7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fc4fc932d2b2aeac431d9c30",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "哗的一声。还有尾巴一甩。",
        "text_hash": "518c3d9c099cc24ca80ae19facc0657971ef5de470274d8adc51fd46561eb196",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_dc63924a64fde85c7e95002d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "然后……",
        "text_hash": "a58d61598889f4d72af91589b63f823ba87de1875c89c8ffc695218280138c83",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c4f8e9841241ecafc84027f1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "杰克高兴地骑在一条鳄鱼背上。",
        "text_hash": "a526ef442a2194f2c14e836546e9bd558668dacd6092d5fcd9a0eeee79643510",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_16162d6ba1f8181707118734",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "杰克的浴缸探险开始了！",
        "text_hash": "9ae8f788e7a3fe4558142904cc8b2a42fdc30e7578e6d5a67684d2dbcb6d5491",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f2aec2dab6d572cb77d49ef9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "杰克注意到灰色水龙头上有什么东西在扭动。",
        "text_hash": "676e5f991d69973eb25997b7a19f27eca089ec98e426232309e72778ec09e19f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_92c0327c21b20bf30ad7ec95",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "快看，什么东西来了！",
        "text_hash": "9665789526db1641605460b9102b3641f5bcdb3f9ae901270f679fc11ee89dc1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_315f9759534190fed9af5ddd",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "它一拧一转……",
        "text_hash": "7495e0ece70612932e68c48b7368bf06b476aaffa818b292968dc9360508b8e6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_41de2b337fd356432a4269fa",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "有什么东西正在长大……",
        "text_hash": "b1e3ad4790fdde179bab6f9c8729314324339020070d9b45507971cb131047c6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d6d182488425dce857c39679",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "它是……",
        "text_hash": "da491fad4e83ab7055d6aa1f02cbeb499c54844f1d815e4cbb074278e16a309f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_aee3b051e60d18cec0d7408f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "杰克站在一头大象背上，大象用水给他冲澡。",
        "text_hash": "e96ed35b8a8eb931ab04f76928c0532111ea4cb4d35433b0adaf73e768e7195b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e6581b8ebce196b368e5c43a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "嘟——！",
        "text_hash": "4117887ca035cba7d19e28d83631b2caac7f2c76945a13c54817d78a0d9b5e6b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_250e2e5f4dacd745d0e62ace",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "从大象背上，杰克注意到一个又长又黄的东西。",
        "text_hash": "a54aca7ea61b46b4290e55983f3e4f631a907f144ddefe8071d91aff3e138938",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0cde51ba5d0fc929150b4e67",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "轰隆一声！",
        "text_hash": "7e695768b4bbd024977a04b83f7a83e660cb7bed1aaf7742028f772ff2148ab5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d662e7ad0a625d93edfcec91",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "向上",
        "text_hash": "0ad9fc2dfddab37f7e15fafc3c0bfeed4db93432a45404a7f7ef6c0f0a050bb9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b4148ec32e9c65b90c8ea122",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "向上",
        "text_hash": "0ad9fc2dfddab37f7e15fafc3c0bfeed4db93432a45404a7f7ef6c0f0a050bb9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_79186d47e64870afcbbad68d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "它在往上升",
        "text_hash": "b9632b0a3c54b562270f65f9954f30652816a10c762fba97ebddc76823f06258",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1b0e3e78a5595bf3b5fa3b28",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "然后……",
        "text_hash": "a58d61598889f4d72af91589b63f823ba87de1875c89c8ffc695218280138c83",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e9e7f04b45f30320f3b5ba9b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "杰克挂在长颈鹿的脖子上荡来荡去。",
        "text_hash": "29f37979ee503fa01fccbfd4cccaeefec5cd8bd615b74b512f5a018752becb7b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_34a2565fb46621bec0e2aee1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "扑通！",
        "text_hash": "51a3b5f84619117745b952d07acc84567edf0ed64ad9b167c41fc21b5d27cc05",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f350b63391ff41f52ddfbe0c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "水里的一块海绵变成了一头河马。",
        "text_hash": "50a2529f7de5c4436e93195ccb7237bd974c4bfe9ed8ad2fbaefdbedb876c219",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b0851c022e74348e043a256b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "哗啦一声。有什么东西冒起泡来。",
        "text_hash": "fe7741f0adc7ce166f1b5b3c1704492d42dd74f3dd34da4af55372e6b530b6e9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6436e900d6dfef99e8150124",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "该是时候……",
        "text_hash": "ca2ee79a5b5647d99db0a5de46677673001988904302d383d22f51a51acfcee6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_daa018ad7db08cd0ddc71b8a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "杰克躺在河马背上晒太阳。从那里他看见了什么橙色的东西。",
        "text_hash": "27e5dca484b386264443ca2af706e54eb108f8bbbd478459317c2103c8f17a30",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d72caed7d6b3a4a7075719cb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "啊啊啊啊啊啊",
        "text_hash": "1a4d34466e268a4693d6a932a9cae2c5ddb9a8f0c5ea39b73b88fb81928e97c1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ee542962d57cc53c44175077",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "但有什么东西正潜伏在后面……",
        "text_hash": "d792de83460b4a823279177cdb100cbb192371d14a56b7da2903edbcc89494b5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_606bc6f63c41ea2f0502f111",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一头狮子吼叫起来。",
        "text_hash": "a1f60e2d40f20f449f50b5ffe22ef4a0ffcbe50e697a538dbf414a0f565a6608",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7d41aa08875f07df78fd2c2f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "吼",
        "text_hash": "72e7891a28bc78a1a29f810cd28775010591ee050a25f519597abac8cf2cdf63",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1f1eb94294c0909d66d1fdda",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "杰克的妈妈站在浴室门口。杰克独自躺在浴缸里。",
        "text_hash": "c6e096e0b01b3077a632c671f18888e198dd6d243f7d6ee0be9f4c2bbf267800",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_69a964500bdc4f7a1738987d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“该出来了。希望你已经洗干净，准备好睡觉了。”",
        "text_hash": "407c617bacd20f0a0af861b72fef8b371ddd6d134385f0263486404a2f85ae8b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2ac292f1da805ce33b98f89b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "杰克已经在床上睡熟了，身边围着他的玩具动物。",
        "text_hash": "94bac0a0169cac5c9840015655609def64c0cda128ad539ad41f343c9ce34238",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_25a530e444859fab0814f882"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
